					<description><![CDATA[I don&#039;t believe that writing gets the credit it deserves for being an art. People have the misconception that writing is easy, probably because everybody has to learn to write at some point in their life. But to bring words to life is an art. There&#039;s no two ways about it. In fact, good writing will allow you to see pictures in your mind which is the definition of art.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I don&#8217;t believe that writing gets the credit it deserves for being an art. People have the misconception that writing is easy, probably because everybody has to learn to write at some point in their life. But to bring words to life is an art. There&#8217;s no two ways about it. In fact, good writing will allow you to see pictures in your mind which is the definition of art.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
